==Arabic==

===Etymology===
From the root verb {{ARchar|[[زوج]]}} (záwwaja), to pair, to couple, to double, verb class VIII {{ARchar|[[ازدوج]]}} (izdáwaja), to be in pairs, to be doubled.

===Adjective===
